# Allowlisting gitignore template for GO projects prevents us
# from adding various unwanted local files, such as generated
# files, developer configurations or IDE-specific files etc.
#
# Recommended: Go.AllowList.gitignore

# Ignore everything
/*

# Claude Code, agents, codex dirs (already ignored by /*, added for clarity)
.agents/
.claude/
.codex/

# But not these files...
!/.gitignore
!/install.sh
!/uninstall.sh
!Dockerfile
!docker-compose.yml
!.github/

!config/
!handlers/
!models/
!services/

!*.go
!go.sum
!go.mod

!**/README.md
!**/LICENSE

!Makefile
!LICENSE

# Binary
model-router
